# Transaction Analysis App: UI Design System

## Color System
- Brand colors:
  - Primary: Blue (#4f46e5)
  - Success: Green (#22c55e)
  - Warning: Yellow (#eab308)
  - Danger: Red (#ef4444)
  - Info: Purple (#8b5cf6)
  
- Semantic colors:
  - Income: Green
  - Expense: Red
  - Transfer: Blue
  - Neutral: Gray

## Typography
- Font family: System default sans-serif
- Size hierarchy:
  - Headings: xl, lg, md
  - Body: base, sm
  - Micro: xs
- Weight:
  - Regular: 400
  - Medium: 500
  - Semibold: 600
  - Bold: 700

## Spacing System
- Based on Tailwind's default scale
- Common patterns:
  - Card padding: p-6
  - Content margin: mb-6
  - Button padding: px-4 py-2
  - Item separation: gap-3

## Component Design

### Cards
- White background
- Rounded corners (rounded-xl)
- Subtle shadow (shadow-md)
- Consistent padding (p-6)

### Buttons
- Text buttons for in-card actions
- Solid buttons for primary actions
- Color indicates purpose (blue: primary, red: destructive)
- Feedback on hover/active states

### Charts
- Consistent size (h-[400px])
- Interactive elements have pointer cursor
- Consistent color scheme across chart types
- Tooltips for detailed information

### Forms
- Clearly labeled fields
- Validation feedback
- Consistent button placement
- Modal container for focus

### Lists
- Virtual rendering for performance
- Clear item separation
- Hover states for interactive items
- Consistent information hierarchy

## Animation Guidelines
- Subtle motion with Framer Motion
- Entry animations for modal dialogs
- Hover transitions for interactive elements
- Loading state animations

## Accessibility Considerations
- Sufficient color contrast
- Keyboard navigation support
- Screen reader friendly labeling
- Focus management in modals

## Responsive Design
- Mobile-first approach
- Flexible layouts using flexbox
- Appropriate spacing on different devices
- Touch-friendly targets on mobile 